  "instructions": [
    "Heat ghee and butter in a pan. ",
    "Add turmeric, garam masala, cumin powder, and red chili powder. ",
    "Cook for 1 minute. ",
    "Add confit tomatoes and cook for 5 minutes. ",
    "Add chicken breasts and cook until browned. ",
    "Add coriander leaves and stir. ",
    "Simmer for 15 minutes. ",
    "Let it rest for 5 minutes before serving. "
